org.apache.distributedlog.api.namespace

Class NamespaceBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.distributedlog.api.namespace.NamespaceBuilder

  • @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Stable
public class NamespaceBuilder
extends Object
    Builder to construct a Namespace. The builder takes the responsibility of loading backend according to the uri.
    Since:
    0.3.32
    See Also:
    Namespace
